Key Match Events: Babar Azam scored 6 off 15 balls while opener Mohammad Rizwan perished for 4 off 4 balls against South Africa at the SCG.
Iftikhar Ahmed and Shadab Khan slammed match-changing half-centuries for Pakistan.
Ahmed scored 51 off 35 balls and Shadab scored 52 off 22 balls, lifting Pakistan to 185-9 in the 20-over contest.
